entries.entry: Learned about collecting user input.  The user input is collected inside of a click event.  The data is sent through a factory function and then sent to a json file.  I was initially having synchronicity issues where the journal was only posting some of the time; I do not yet fully understand how the fix worked.  I intend this weekend to gain a better understanding of asynchronous code.
